headline: JPMorgan’s (JPM) 2026 Net Interest Income Growth Remained a Key Focus at Truist
summary: JPMorgan Chase & Co. (NYSE:JPM) ranks among the best financial stocks to buy according to billionaire Israel Englander. On January 14, Truist Securities boosted its price target for JPMorgan Chase & Co. (NYSE:JPM) to $334 from $331 while keeping a Hold rating.
